    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors are appropriately not assessed per ASME V&V 40 Table 3 for MRL 2. Discretization error and output comparison results confirm the CFD model is sufficiently credible to support the regulatory decision that RH < 1 under worst-case CPB operating conditions. The power-law hemolysis model is accepted as the standard formulation for this device class. Assessment team concludes the model credibility is adequate for the stated COU.",
